item.title: I need help im new!
item.dc:creator: @jme jme
item.description:
@jme wrote:

Rofl, yes I think we can see you really are new

You do not need scar or aryan to use moparscape.

Scar is a colorpicker. It finds color's on runescape and clicks them, thus automating tasks. It is very undetectable although that depends entirely on the script.

Aryan clicks using object ID's, it's very detectable so use it ony on throw away accounts. However, it is very effective on making quick cash.

Moparscape is a private server client. Go to the server delveopment section, and it's stickied right at the top
You'll have to find a server IP, use the search button on these forums to find one.
